## Superseded from mojo-exotic-dtype-default-param-crash

```yaml
name: mojo-exotic-dtype-default-param-crash
description: "Fix Mojo 0.26.1 ASAN abort at module load from exotic dtype (E8M0, FP8) used as default parameter values."
category: debugging
date: 2026-03-27
version: "1.0.0"
user-invocable: false
tags: [mojo, asan, dtype, e8m0, fp8, default-param, module-load]
```

Default params are evaluated at module load. Scalar[E8M0](1.0) has no valid float cast path.
Fix: bitcast-safe alias using exponent encoding. E8M0_ONE = exponent 127; FP8_ONE = 0x3C.
PR #5177 on ProjectOdyssey.

