## Superseded from mojo-print-effective-target-codegen-diagnostic

```yaml
name: mojo-print-effective-target-codegen-diagnostic
description: "First-line no-compile diagnostic for 'wrong instructions emitted on this host' Mojo reports..."
category: debugging
date: 2026-05-12
version: "1.0.0"
user-invocable: false
verification: verified-local
tags: [mojo, target-cpu, target-features, print-effective-target, codegen,
       host-fingerprinting, cpu-detection, avx-512, sigill, modular-6413, diagnostic]
```

`mojo build --print-effective-target <some.mojo>` prints driver-resolved --target-cpu and
--target-features without compiling. Verified on hermes (Lunar Lake, no AVX-512) and
epimetheus (Skylake, no AVX-512). Cross-check against /proc/cpuinfo. PR #5401.

