## Superseded from mojo-retry-pattern-ci-validator

```yaml
name: mojo-retry-pattern-ci-validator
description: 'Detect bare pixi run mojo test/run/build/package calls in GitHub Actions workflows not wrapped in a retry loop.'
category: ci-cd
date: 2026-03-15
version: 1.0.0
user-invocable: false
```

Python validator script (validate_mojo_retry_pattern.py) that audits GHA workflow files.
COMPILING_SUBCOMMANDS = {test, run, build, package}; RETRY_MARKERS = ("while [", "attempt=").
Handles echo/comment false positives and docker run continuation lines.
26 workflows audited, 0 violations. PR #4839, issue #3955.

