## Superseded from mojo-runtime-crash-bisection

```yaml
name: mojo-runtime-crash-bisection
description: 'Systematic approach for bisecting Mojo runtime crashes to create minimal reproducers...'
category: debugging
date: 2026-03-16
version: 1.0.0
user-invocable: false
```

7-step binary reduction methodology: characterize → reduce scope → reduce ops → reduce struct →
verify user code → inline deps → file upstream. Key: List[Int] field in struct triggers heap
corruption; function scope (not inline main) required. Minimum config: 32x32, 16 channels, 2 conv layers.
Filed modular/modular#6187.

---

