## Superseded from mojo-serialization-ci-crash

```yaml
name: mojo-serialization-ci-crash
description: 'Debug Mojo serialization CI crashes from dtype string conversion mismatches and Python interop crashes.'
category: debugging
date: 2026-03-07
version: 1.0.0
user-invocable: false
```

Two independent bugs: (1) String(dtype) vs dtype_to_string(dtype) mismatch in save_tensor();
(2) Python.import_module("pathlib").glob crashes CI → replace with os.listdir + insertion sort.
Crash log shows "Testing hex encoding..." before the real crash — misleading; real crash is
from Python interop initialization. Always check git diff origin/main before investigating.

