## Superseded from mojo-transient-crash-rerun

```yaml
name: mojo-transient-crash-rerun
description: 'Identify and clear transient Mojo runner crashes in CI by re-triggering failed jobs.'
category: ci-cd
date: 2026-03-06
version: 1.0.0
user-invocable: false
```

Three-check confirmation: (1) stack frames only from runtime libs (no repo files),
(2) same test group passes on main same date, (3) PR has no logic changes.
Fix: gh run rerun <RUN_ID> --repo <REPO> --failed. PR #3288, issue #3074.

