## Superseded from preexisting-flaky-crash-rerun

```yaml
name: preexisting-flaky-crash-rerun
description: 'Diagnose whether CI failures are pre-existing flaky crashes unrelated to PR changes.'
category: ci-cd
date: 2026-03-06
version: 1.0.0
user-invocable: false
```

Quick path: gh pr diff <PR_NUMBER> --name-only → check if failing test files are in the diff.
If not, confirm with recent successful main CI run, then re-trigger with --failed.
If crashes persist: open tracking issue, do NOT block PR merge. PR #3355, issue #3157.
